import React, { useState, useEffect } from 'react'; import { Link, useNavigate, useLocation } from 'react-router-dom'; import { useAuth } from '../context/AuthContext'; import { MessageCircle, FileText, Brain, Calendar, LogOut, TrendingUp, Clock, BookOpen, Award, Settings, Bell, Search, BarChart3, Users, Zap, Sparkles, CheckCircle2, CalendarDays, ArrowUpRight, Menu, X } from 'lucide-react'; const Dashboard = () => { const { user, logout } = useAuth(); const navigate = useNavigate(); const [stats, setStats] = useState({ totalDocuments: 0, totalChats: 0, quizzesGenerated: 0, studyPlans: 0 }); const [recentActivity, setRecentActivity] = useState([]); const [upcomingSessions, setUpcomingSessions] = useState([]); const [learningMilestones, setLearningMilestones] = useState([]); const [resourceHighlights, setResourceHighlights] = useState([]); const [insights, setInsights] = useState([]); const [loading, setLoading] = useState(true); useEffect(() => { loadDashboardData(); }, []); const loadDashboardData = async () => { try { setStats({ totalDocuments: 12, totalChats: 45, quizzesGenerated: 8, studyPlans: 3 }); setRecentActivity([ { id: 1, type: 'chat', title: 'Discussed Machine Learning concepts', time: '2 hours ago', icon: MessageCircle }, { id: 2, type: 'quiz', title: 'Generated quiz on Data Structures', time: '5 hours ago', icon: Brain }, { id: 3, type: 'document', title: 'Uploaded "Advanced Algorithms.pdf"', time: '1 day ago', icon: FileText }, { id: 4, type: 'plan', title: 'Created study plan for Finals', time: '2 days ago', icon: Calendar } ]); setInsights([ { id: 1, title: 'Study streak', value: '7 days', change: '+2 vs last week', icon: Clock, accent: 'bg-orange-100 text-orange-600' }, { id: 2, title: 'Average quiz score', value: '82%', change: '+5% improvement', icon: Brain, accent: 'bg-purple-100 text-purple-600' }, { id: 3, title: 'AI sessions this week', value: '12', change: 'Up 36% week-over-week', icon: MessageCircle, accent: 'bg-blue-100 text-blue-600' } ]); setUpcomingSessions([ { id: 1, title: 'Review Machine Learning notes', description: 'Deep dive into gradient boosting and ensembles', when: 'Tomorrow · 09:00 AM', category: 'Focus Session' }, { id: 2, title: 'Quiz retake: Data Structures', description: 'Attempt the adaptive quiz to reinforce weak topics', when: 'Friday · 04:30 PM', category: 'Assessment' }, { id: 3, title: 'Upload lecture summaries', description: 'Digitize week 6 lecture notes for AI enrichment', when: 'Saturday · 11:00 AM', category: 'Preparation' } ]); setLearningMilestones([ { id: 1, title: 'Complete Data Structures summary', progress: 68, eta: 'Due today', icon: BookOpen }, { id: 2, title: 'Finalize AI research outline', progress: 42, eta: 'Due in 3 days', icon: Brain }, { id: 3, title: 'Revise calculus flashcards', progress: 85, eta: 'On track', icon: Award } ]); setResourceHighlights([ { id: 1, title: 'Algorithms cheat sheet.pdf', category: 'Document · 2.4 MB', link: '/documents', icon: FileText, accent: 'text-blue-600' }, { id: 2, title: 'AI Tutor conversation history', category: 'Chat · Last session 2h ago', link: '/chat', icon: MessageCircle, accent: 'text-emerald-600' }, { id: 3, title: 'Weekly study plan', category: 'Planner · Updated yesterday', link: '/chat', icon: Calendar, accent: 'text-indigo-600' } ]); setLoading(false); } catch (error) { console.error('Failed to load dashboard data:', error); setLoading(false); } }; const handleChatClick = () => { navigate('/chat', { state: { messageType: 'chat' } }); }; const handleQuizClick = () => { navigate('/chat', { state: { messageType: 'quiz' } }); }; const handleStudyPlanClick = () => { navigate('/chat', { state: { messageType: 'study-plan' } }); }; const statCards = [ { id: 'documents', label: 'Total Documents', value: stats.totalDocuments, change: '+3 this week', icon: FileText, gradient: 'from-blue-500 to-blue-600', chip: 'text-blue-600 bg-blue-100' }, { id: 'chats', label: 'Chat Sessions', value: stats.totalChats, change: '+12 this week', icon: MessageCircle, gradient: 'from-emerald-500 to-emerald-600', chip: 'text-emerald-600 bg-emerald-100' }, { id: 'quizzes', label: 'Quizzes Generated', value: stats.quizzesGenerated, change: '85% avg score', icon: Brain, gradient: 'from-purple-500 to-purple-600', chip: 'text-purple-600 bg-purple-100' }, { id: 'plans', label: 'Study Plans', value: stats.studyPlans, change: '2 active plans', icon: Calendar, gradient: 'from-amber-500 to-orange-500', chip: 'text-amber-600 bg-amber-100' } ]; if (loading) { return (
